gomodel:SYNGO_1673  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: A total of 296 proteins were identified in a PSD preparation from forebrain or cerebellum by LC-MS/MS. Among these SPARC (found as \"secreted acidic cysteine rich glycoprotein\") was identified.\nAs SPARC is generally described as extracellular matrix components we consider the protein as part of the perisynaptic or synaptic extracellular matrix.. Experimental description: \"PSD fractions were prepared from rat forebrains and cerebellum ...\", p. 1159" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0269-0311" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9681-3318" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9880-1214" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9377-7414" ;
